          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Add a knob of <strong>butter</strong>, the <strong>chopped chives</strong> and a grind of<strong> pepper</strong> to the <strong>drained potatoes</strong> and give everything a good mix up – these are your <strong>herby potatoes</strong></p>",
      "order": 7,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/1765.-step-7-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
